1.7.3 Contents of a Job Advertisement 
The job advertisement shall contain:
a) A brief about MUBS; 
b) The job title; 
c) Job salary scale; 
d) Allowances and other benefits; 
e) Reporting hierarchy; 
f) Overall Objective of the job; 
g) Job description; 
h) Job and person specifications; 
i) Application procedure; 
j) Closing date for applications. 
1.8  Application 
The job application shall include: 
a) The application letter; 
b) Copies of relevant academic/professional transcripts & 
certificates;
c) Detailed curriculum vitae;
d) Names and addresses of referees; 
e) Applicant’s physical address, telephone contact, and 
email address; 
f) Any other relevant information.
